snippet.title: Adrullan Online Adventures
snippet.description:
Visit us at www.adrullan.online !
Adrullan Online Adventures is a voxel based standalone MMORPG built from the ground up in the Unity Engine. A world of adventure and excitement awaits you in Adrullan! Returning to the classic roots of the MMORPG genre, Adrullan Online Adventures is designed to be a demanding yet rewarding multiplayer experience.
